She looked at Phobia, "Thanks for all your help Phobia.  I may need 
more of it in the near future.  Thanks again."
she watched the spider leave.  She scratched  her neck, for some 
reason, it had been itching unmercifully lately.

She looked at the plans and waited for the other bots to enter her 
room.
